                            <div class="widget-title">
                                <h6>Welcome to AADCO!</h6>
                            </div>
                            <p>Since 1985, AADCO Medical, Inc. has specialized in the design and manufacture of Medical Imaging products for distribution both domestically and internationally, presenting the industry’s most versatile group of Ergonomic Safety Products and Solutions for Medical Imaging.</p>
                            <br />
                            <p>Our innovative product line includes the highly esteemed ErgoLite®, a radiation protection apron proven to reduce career shortening stress injuries. All of AADCO’s lead protection garments are manufactured at our corporate headquarters in the heart of Vermont.</p>
                            <br />
                            <p>AADCO is also the manufacturer of the world’s only MRI-Safe™ Overhead Suspension Systems, as well as hundreds of other innovative equipment and accessory products dedicated to imaging, including a wide variety of X-Ray Protective Garments, Eyewear, Conventional and MRI-Safe® Barriers, Shields and Systems, Lighting and Sterile / Disposable Surgical Products.</p>
